title: Nine Inch Nails With Teeth Tour Live in Buenos Aires CD-1 12/01/
description:
Nine Inch Nails With Teeth Tour Live in Buenos Aires CD-1
Amazing NIN performance in Buenos Aires/Argentina
Line up:
 Trent Reznor
 Aaron North
 Alessandro Cortini
 Alex Carapetis (yes!! hehe)
 Jeordie White

Cd-1 track list:
You know what you are?
Terrible Lie
The line begins to blur
March of the pigs
Something I can never have
The frail
The wretched
Closer
Burn
Gave up
With teeth
Wish
Only

Video quality is fine
Sound quality mmm.. if you are NIN fan you wouldn&#039;t have any problem, I would say 6.5/10 

You can download the dvd cover here: http://www.nin.com.ar/portada.rar   

All credits to SOULMANAGER, he&#039;s the main mentor of this dvd.
Special thanks to Nati!!!
Also thanks to old nin-latinamerica forum members, those that could make this distribution possible :)
